---
title: Anushka's Creamy Dauphinoise Cottage Pie with Beef, Carrot and Italian Style Cheese
description: Anushka’s Creamy Dauphinoise Cottage Pie with Beef, Carrot and Italian Style Cheese has been specially selected as part of our Chef’s Pick recipe range. Hearty and warming, cottage pie - in Anushka’s words - is “a hug on a plate”, and this dish combines those traditional flavours together with creamy dauphinoise. A super tasty addition to your midweek menu on cold winter nights.
